Your Birthdate: October 7
Born on the 7th day of month gives you a tendency to be something of a perfectionist and makes you more individualistic in many ways. Your mind is good at deep mental analysis and complicated reasoning. You are very psychic and sensitive, and you should usually follow your hunches. You may not take orders too well, so you may want to work alone or in a situation where you can be the boss. This birthday gives a tendency to be somewhat self-centered and a little stubborn.
What Does Your Birth Date Mean?

Yeah.. I feel like crap. I went home as of lunch and then my mom plugged my head with tylenol and zyrtec and robitussion(however spelt) now my heads spinning and I really just want to go back to sleep. I miss Daniel. I made him lunch today and I hope he liked it, I also made my lunch but I for got it at home Sandwiches can be awesome. I also made some chocolate milk for lunch too! Damn that sucks. but yeah, now I'm stuck over at kathleen's appartment with cable two pugs and a computer. I took a nap but that just made me feel even more miserable. I've been watch the all day Hannible marathon yeah.. not too good. but yeah.. I feel as if people wouldn't even read to this part so.. I'm just gonna .. yeah laytah.

cking suicidal thoughts have come back into my mind. Everything is starting to turn back into what it was. I feel like a huge fuck-up in everything. Even though I catch my self laughing for some reason these thoughts still come back. Today my grandma was supposed to come back to the house to get some of her things that she left. but really she came to check on the house, and I took care of it but.. she doesn't know that I live alone. and yeah.. my mom is gonna move back in here next weekend... I know she has the right to and it should be great to actually see her but.. we can barely stand each other for an hour let alone her trying to get back into the routine of controlling my life, of which was going somewhat fine at least better than before she mentioned that she would be coming back. I won't be able to do all the things I really want to do. Things with Daniel haven't really been going too well either. Yeah we get to occasionally spend time together but thats only when he can fit me into his schedual. I never really feel like he tries to see me.. I always have to ask him to come over to see him, and he rarely spends the night anymore. I don't know what happened he still says he loves me, but I don't always feel it when he says things like that to me. We have to always ask for hugs and kisses rather just giving them freely. We always end up argeing whic I feel is my fault cause I think I might be getting a little paranoid. which is the stupidest shit. and the sad thing is that I don't have any real best friends. I have friends that I hangout with at school and thats awesome cause thats basically the only times I ever catch me smiling and laughing. but I never really hangout with anyone. Everyone has grown apart, and it sucks. all this stress and depression makes me sick, and I just want to end it all. god, i hate sounding so fucking Emo. But Damit. Life has yet to fuckign prove to me that it sucks yet again. and i swear this is not the last time. oh no, its not the last time.

Libra
(September 23 - October 22)
As this is the sign that rules marriage, Librans are definitely cut out for it. They're capable of making the associated adjustments, and of sacrificing some of their own desires to accommodate their beloved. They're also very romantic! Librans tend to define themselves by their relationships, and thus they don't feel complete without one.

well, yeah. Today was kinda weird. Well, It started off this morning I slept over at Daniels house I first woke uparound 6:30 am and his alarm clock went off but he didn't wae up so I ended up somehow sleeping through the alarm an waking up a half an hour later and told him to shut it off and that it was time to get up well, sorry I'm taking so long but we ended up waking up around 8am or 8:10 am anyways we got up he called in cause he needed to go to the doctor. then he ended up taking his sister to work and dropping me off at school but not leaving till after he talks to his old friends. then I went to school dressed in his etallica shirt that he gave to me the night before. I went into class and started to dress out for Dance then all the sudden I heard brit say something like someone go hit, it ended up being a phyk.(badspelling!) patient from up stairs who was running away and ran into the road and got hit she was still alive and yeah everything was all as well as it could have been. then we wet over our Dance which took a litte ime cause wen had to incorperate Carli into the dance then... after that then went to adv. bio./chem. of which I didn't have my stuff for cause I slept a daniels. then after school Daniel came to pick me up and we went to his siter's work cause she needed lunch. We went and got lunch ( of which tader tots are the best) then he took me home where I ate more.( god, I really am gonna become a fat ass,just sooner than I thought.)well, anyways I tookanap and woke up arund 7:30pm and I got calls from Daniel, and then  got online and I saw that my mom's GF sent me an E-mail telling me that there were these two cats looking for a home!!!! I automatically got offline and called Kath and yay! I get to hve two cats. Yay!I'm so excited( sorry I made you go through my whole ay and I'm sorythat Idon't write things well, caue really it wasn't that boring of a day) but yeah anyways. One is a boy and his name is fearless, and they said hes more of a people person and, the other one is a girl and her name is Tannah, and she likes to hide. but they're around 9 years old and they've lived together for just about hat long so thay don't want to seperate them, and the only people that have responded is no kill shelters and a woman who has a child , but she only want one of them, and then Me. Yay! I'm so excited. I used to have a cat his name was Chaos but my brothers girlfriend took it. and now its living with them up in flagstaff where its freezing its ass off, and now its not a people cat anymore. it stays up stairs and last time I visited I only got to see it for like 10 seconds. but yeah.. chaos was born on my back poarch and he had a bad eye so... I took him in and plnned to only have him till his eye was better but that all of his seven brothers and sisters showed up and they were all so cute. I wanted to keep all of them, but my mom didn't like the Idea. but they kept coming to my front poarch and I fed them and I would take chaos outside and let him play with his bros and sistahs but then one day they all never came back.I got so sad. but.. Chaos's eye got better and him and Padre kept each other company and they liked toplay around. it was so cute. but yeah...Omg I'm so excited. If any of you have a cat that you can't have or you're moving and can't take with you. seriously I'll take it in I love cats. (sigh) not that anyone still reads the crap I write but.. anyways talk to you kids laytah.

So yeah.. shit has gone down. One of my pugs died on wednesday. She some how got out of the yard at Kath's house and got ran over by a car. Not only that.. one of my boss's osthe ten year old daughter last night due to a drunken driver. I don't really know how to react. I started crying earlier when I was looking at artwork made by kath's student in tribute to Olive. it was just soo sweet. and I really want to make my boss a card not that it'll help but..I want her to know that she has support. 

  I keep hearing weird noises arond my house. I kinda feel tht its because one of my neighbors moved away. They always brought me comfort being in the house alone. Living alone is starting to get to me. Everyone has someone to look foreward to or not look foreward to when they come home. I have nothing.

     eh.. I'm too tired to type. No one really reads these anyways.

last night I could berely sleep. I would literaly wake up every 20 min. Eventually it lengthened out to every hour but the last dream that I had freaked me out and made me not want to go back to sleep. 
It started out with My dad his girlfriend and her two kids went to a party at one of my mom's either brother or sister's house, which was really weird cause why would they invite dad along?but anyways... we went to the party and everyone was chatting all the little kids were running around, and every once in a while you'd hear one of them screaming because they raninto a wall or something. My dad was in the corner( being bored) and picking out blue candies out of the candy jar. there was also an insanely large bowl of gummy Life Savers( of which I used to love ) so.. when I first went over there I took only a few and sat down and just as I got back up to get more one of my aunts or uncles(is that how you spell it?)anyways... shouted out to the kids that there were goodies on the table. and at first it didn't strike me that it was the gummy life savers that I was going for. So like a stampede they trampled me at first but then I funght back to get the last three gummy Life savers. and to savor the life savers I went outside only to find chester.(I wasn't too dreake out but I now cue as to how she found out where one of my family members lives.) we talked for a little bit ony to settle on the Idea that she was going tospend te night that night. so I went back in to tell my dad that I was going to the house cause chester wanted to come over.( and Chester was stil ot side waiting for me.) and probably less than 5 secs. of walking inside the front door my uncle David told me that none of my family members liked me, and wanted me to leave.(!!!!!!!) WHAT KIND OF A FAMILY DO I HAVE HERE? and what knd of a family would say that to someone? anyways... I could see that my dad was still sitting in the chair in the corner next to the jar of candies and empty bowl which used to hold Lifesavers.but he did nothin. He didn't say anything he just sat there and continually sorted the blue candies out of the jar. and his girlfriend Tammy was on the floor playing with all the kids( cause thats her profession, shes a professional babysitter) and she didn't even realize what was just said.  So.. of course I was pissed. So... I yelled out to my family" Is this ow everyone feels?" and I got one of the worst responses in my whoe entire life. They kinda had this order of coming to me from where ever they were in the house and told me to leave. and make it easier on everybody. Well why the hell should I make it easier on you when you are all ganging up on me?(deep breath) then I made a statement about one of my aunts of which I was told that she would not be at the party and I got the feeling that she would never give up on me. Even if she wasn't of actual blood realation. I said something along the lines of" If she were her she would help me." and I looked down and she was sitting right there and she basically just rolled her eyesin away I'v never imagined that eyes can be rolled. So I said F* this and stormed out to find Chester right there. She saw that something was wrong but she didn't want to ask.I realized that I had no shoes on so... I walked back inside to get my sandals and for some reason I wore socks with them cause when I tryed to turn my sock right side out a shit load of gummy life savers fell out and after that a shit load of blue candies came after. My dad started laughing. Everyone else looked at me like What the F*. so I threw the sock grabbed my sandals and slamed the door only to find my mom right in my face and she tryed grabbing me. Kinda like the grabbing where people grabb you on the arms and you have no control. and told her to let me go causeI waspissed off that she wasn't there for me. No one was. Chester wasn't even outside anymore. So... yeah.. I guess my body couldn't take any more pressure from the dream or from the fact that I'm/soon not going to be, severely sick. but yeah I woke up in a sweat. I haven't sweat for a dream in a long time. I woke up with tears coming out of my eyes and I'm now afraid to talk to anyone in my family cause I always fet like they ere hiding something before cause we're not as close as a family should/could be. but yeah.... I don't know.

wow!Ir's been forever since I've updated. Not that anyone would want to read this shit but... anyways. Yeah, I'm back at Metro and I'm so glad. So many beautiful peole with awesome personalities.Yeah... I'm Still in Ballet 3-4 but its dance so... I could careless. I love how Nicole and Lisa teach the class. I'm also in Physical Express with Nicole. Who happens to love to work out, and somehow I have no clue how she can do this but she can talk and yell and do whatever while working out during the class and thats not the onlyclass that she teaches. but yeah enough about that.... 
I'm in Vocal this year with Stephan who just happens to e one of the most layed back teachers in my life. and not that I don't like that but I wish we got my work done. We have too many Noisey people who just bitch and bitch at eachother is like .... ooo I wish I had the ballsto just slap every single one of them on the face and them kick them in there oddly proportioned ass. Damn. But I love Stephan. I love his look on lfe and I think he is the only one besides Jeremy that I can take on peoples views on Politics.
But yeah... Its sucks right now... Cause my throat is swollen like a motha F*ckah. I can berely talk anymore. Like yesterday I was kind of alright but.. today.... wow. I berely movemy neck it hurts soo much. and I have yet to eat ANYTHING in two days. It sucks cause I LOVE FOOD! but yeah I keep getting these on and off fevers and yeah that really sucks, well besides the fact tht it makes me want to sit in the bathtub all day. but My Air conditioning berely working....


yeah I got to cut this one shrt for now.
later kiddos!

So... I actually went to school today. YAY! I was so happy and so excited. I saw old teachers new kids, old friends and everyone was so happy and cheery. Then I saw an old friend from Central that I used to party with and she told me on how she had seen my recent ex and yeah ...that just brought the whole day down. There is just some ties between me and him and I'm so ready to get on with my life but I know I won't be able to do that untill I've talked to him. But I'm not sure if I'm ready to confront him, face-to-face. At the time being at school I didn't feel it was right to talk about it cause I felt that if I did then I would burst into tears and I really don't want to be remembered for that.

But yeah after school Alex, and I went to the Willow House and got some Pita and hummus. WOW! I was so happy. That was the best meal I've had in a long time. We were sitting there for a while and just talking and a discussion about him came up. We sat there for a while and I can't beleive how long we talking about this subject. I was astounded that she would let me talk about it. With alot of other people its kinda a touchy subject like some I know don't want to hear anything about this guy ad in a major way I can totally understand but I needed to get this out of me. It wasn't any better of a place but it was more comfortable( somehow). We ended up swapping stories which made it easier for me to bare and not pour my eyes out. but after leaving the Willow house we ended up going to Metro mall, to look for a back pack for alex, we ended up finding her lik 4 pairs of pants andtwo shirts and a small bag.

After a couple of hours at the mall with Alex spending more on clothes in one day than I could spend in one year. I ended up going home to find that I saw a familiar name on the callerID and It was Nicole Staron, but it wasn't actually her who called, But "HE". So.. She told me all this crap that he and his little buddy were doin. and it seems like he really wants to get a hold of me. For what I don't know but.. I don't know how this is gonna end start or even happen. I have no clue of where he is gonna pop out of and I'm scared to go anywhere that we went together which is kinda like everywhere. 

But yeah I just want to thank Jeremy, and Alex for both bein there to talk to. Hope to see you guys tommorow.  Yay! yoga tommorow!

Every time I drive by or get on a bus, or see a similarity on the person walking down the street I always look and see if he's there. I don' t know if I want him to be there or if I'm afraid. The last time I saw him was on the bus. I felt like I was gonna throw up when I saw him get on. I didn't want him to see me cause I didn't expect to see him. I felt as if I was ready for it. So many things were goin on wit us it was unreal. 

Well yeah...school starts tommorow. I'm so nervous. I hope everything goes well.
Got to go to sleep.

Damn Emotion! Why does it have to strike you so hard. I miss the days when it was alright ot be careless about anything. Last night was hard. I fell asleep crying, I have these two different people stuck in my head and what they did to me. They've both hurt me, and I don't even see them anymore but I guess thats part of the reason it hurts. 

Its all a triangle, My own flesh and blood won't get over the fact that I went out with one of his old friends that he now hates, Even though he went out with now three people of my relation, two of with I have been close with, and the other not as much. He thinks that I shouldn't use that as an excuse, but now that the two that I was close with no longer talk to me and he dosen't want me to say it was him. He dosen't want me to be able to fight back with truthful facts that he can no longer fight against.

The other is just the one my brother hates. In a way I hate him my self, but then for some stupid reason I still have feelings for him. I don't even know if I should feel anything. Technically, we're not boken up, but we might as well be. Hes sleeping around with other little girls, of whom of which I feel extremly sorry for. I feel bad that I wasn't there to warn them about him. His actions. His Drugs. His Abuse. Why did I let him do that to me? Why did I defend him and push precious friends away? Why do I still care? Why should I care?

Why is it when little girls get told to not get into trouble, they go looking for it?

YAY!!! I'm into Metro. YAY!!!! I'm soo happy. Thank you soo much Jeremy if it wasn't for you , I don't think I would have gone. It was scary and stressful but....I'm in. YAY!
